title: The Feud Continues
description:
Justin is not letting go of his grudge against Chris (00:02:00) and reveals he noticed Chris is deleting bad reviews from his new podcast. A new date for the Wilbur will be announced very soon. 'A Theater Near Me' is doing bonus episodes before it even launches (00:23:30). CNN & Dr. Fauci want Jesse Waters fired over out of context "kill shot" and "ambush" comments (00:31:00). Tom Brady and Jim Gray bring on Andrea Bocelli to their podcast (00:43:17). A Billboard Chart Guy reunion (01:07:00). John Amos returns (01:35:00). A Chris Christmas-ish game & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
